==English==
===Etymology===
[[scan]] + ''o'', by analogy with '''[[typo]]''', as if this were formed a similar way from '''[[type]]'''

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}<!-- not 'scannoes', again by analogy from 'typo' -->
# A typographical error introduced by optical character recognition ([[OCR]]) software, which may mistake a letter or set of letters for a letter or set of letters of similar shape, as ''[[tum]]'' for ''[[turn]]'', or ''[[google:Dosition|Dosition]]'' for ''[[position]].''

